#Getting and Cleaning Data Project

##Description
This file is for providing additional information about the variables, data and transformations used in the course project.

##Attribute Information
For each record in the dataset it is provided:

Triaxial acceleration from the accelerometer (total acceleration) and the estimated body acceleration.
Triaxial Angular velocity from the gyroscope.
A 561-feature vector with time and frequency domain variables.
Its activity label.
An identifier of the subject who carried out the experiment.

##Variables
1. x_train, y_train, x_test, y_test, subject_train and subject_test contain the data from the downloaded files.
2. data_x, data_y and data_sub merge the datasets for further use.
3. features contain the corrected column names.
4. data_all merges data_x, data_y and data_subject in a big dataset.
5. at last avg_data contains the averages that are stored in avg_data.txt
